**Request Interceptor:**
```typescript
// Add auth token to all requests
axiosClient.interceptors.request.use(config => {
  const token = globalStore[GlobalStoreFieldE.AUTH_TOKEN].value;
  if (token) {
    config.headers.Authorization = `Bearer ${token}`;
  }
  return config;
});
```

**Response Interceptor:**
```typescript
